  "description": "Benchmark scores — VALUE instances of the evaluation broad_category (SUB08). Each entry is a BenchmarkScore container that links to a Model (via SCORED_ON MOR14), a Task (via EVALUATES_TASK MOR15), and a Suite (via BENCHMARKED_BY MOR16).",
